{
  "stem": "7739.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 1.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we worked in these-- in retrospect, I think now because we had these ammunition factories, about 3,000-- approximately 3,000 Jews from our town were able to work there and, therefore, bide or buy our time, to-- for tomorrow, for tomorrow, hoping that things will improve and the war will end.",
      "word_count": 51
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] We got, more or less, used to camp life.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You-- there was no time for mourning.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, you had to work and work hard.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You had to account for yourself.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Jews were expendable.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We-- in the camp, there were only Jews.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "At work, we mixed with the general working population, which, of course, some of the Gentiles were friends with whom my father had dealings with.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Amongst who, because he worked there before the expulsion, and because he was, more or less, able to foretell or maybe have some kind of inkling that things weren't always going to be like this, he gave some-- he gave to some of his friends or acquaintances or coworkers money, or maybe he gave them some valuables.",
      "word_count": 57
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I'm not so sure.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And after the expulsion, when we weren't going-- able to go home again, although we were living in the same town, the vicinity, our accommodation was the-- the camp, which was, of course, surrounded by barbed wire and watchtowers with Ukrainian guards.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You could only go and come under armed guard.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And at work, since we were mixing with the general population, if you had friends there, it was a help.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Some people were quite honorable.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And my father was able to acquire from them, say, if he gave-- if he gave somebody, say, 100 to 200 zlotys.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
